00:19:12,030 --> 00:19:12,670
Supervisor Li,

390
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,444
Secretary Han is out on official duty.

391
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:16,355
He'll be back by the Shen hour.

392
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,480
Please wait here.

