00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:26,060
(Ministry of Justice)

394
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,110
Liangyuan?

395
00:19:51,333 --> 00:19:52,933
When did you return to Chang'an?

396
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,644
Is your mission as the Litchi Envoy

397
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:59,244
going smoothly?

398
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,240
Oh right.

399
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:06,000
Liangyuan.

400
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:06,840
