424
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:01,400
Liangyuan, after you left,

425
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:05,510
we all missed you.

426
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,270
We all hoped

427
00:21:07,270 --> 00:21:09,400
you'd succeed

428
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:12,200
and bring honor to the Shanglin Office.

429
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:18,680
If you're facing any problems,

430
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,790
you must speak up.

431
00:21:22,688 --> 00:21:24,466
What you're going through now

432
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,933
could well be our future.

433
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:31,270
We'll definitely support you.

434
00:21:47,955 --> 00:21:49,777
I'm fine. You go on.

435
00:21:56,444 --> 00:21:57,520
Supervisor Song.

436
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,080
Do you...

437
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,920
Do you know anyone

438
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,240
who can help me

439
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:08,644
get this litchi delivery petition
submitted?

440
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,510
This is ridiculous!

441
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:16,070
Li Shande has already found

442
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:17,480
a method to transport litchis.

443
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:19,350
However, these offices

444
00:22:19,422 --> 00:22:21,577
still won't accept it
and stall the progress.

445
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:27,440
It was also them

446
00:22:27,844 --> 00:22:30,030
who pushed
the litchi envoy mission around,

447
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:30,790
that's how

448
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:32,288
it landed on us.

449
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:35,822
These shameless rascals.

450
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,400
I know them too well.

451
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,480
Liangyuan,

452
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,590
what's your plan?

453
00:22:51,844 --> 00:22:54,377
The litchi delivery can't proceed

454
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:57,177
without official approval.

455
00:22:58,310 --> 00:22:59,150
So I came

456
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,110
to ask

457
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,270
if you know anyone

458
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,911
who can help submit this petition.

459
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,310
If we submit it

460
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:12,711
through the Shanglin Office,

461
00:23:13,244 --> 00:23:15,177
it's likely to get us the cold shoulder.

462
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:20,950
Mr. Qu,

463
00:23:21,266 --> 00:23:23,866
doesn't your brother serve
at the Ministry of Personnel?

464
00:23:24,333 --> 00:23:25,555
Could he help?

465
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,320
Sir,

466
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,920
my brother is a director,

467
00:23:31,177 --> 00:23:32,377
and submitting a petition

468
00:23:32,377 --> 00:23:33,600
would be easy for him,

469
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,000
but unfortunately,

470
00:23:35,666 --> 00:23:36,880
he just left for Luoyang

471
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:39,160
on duty earlier today.

472
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:41,600
He won't be back until next month.

473
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:42,800
Liangyuan,

474
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,555
can you wait?

475
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:45,600
I can't.

476
00:23:48,765 --> 00:23:50,285
If you'd come to me yesterday,

477
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:51,150
it might've worked.

478
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,320
Oh right.

479
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:58,000
I have a relative
at the Imperial Library.

480
00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:58,910
He

481
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:01,720
handles logistics.

482
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,777
I can ask him.

483
00:24:04,070 --> 00:24:05,110
The Imperial Library

484
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:06,550
deals with books.

485
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,350
Actually,

486
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:15,933
I have a connection.

487
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:18,880
It's my classmate.

488
00:24:19,133 --> 00:24:21,800
He just got promoted to recorder
at the Imperial Household Department.

489
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:23,960
I can pay him a visit

490
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:25,440
and see if

491
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,533
he can do me this favor.

492
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:27,590
I've tried that.

493
00:24:28,350 --> 00:24:30,550
They handle tributes
from foreign states.

494
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,888
What I'm working on
is litchis from Lingnan.

495
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,000
The Shanglin Office

496
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,440
has no real power.

497
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:45,550
To put it plainly,

498
00:24:46,510 --> 00:24:49,311
we grow flowers and trees.

499
00:24:50,030 --> 00:24:51,640
We've seen a lot of

500
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,240
influential officials

501
00:24:53,590 --> 00:24:55,155
at Leyou Gaden,

502
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:57,160
but we never

503
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,790
knew them.

504
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:01,640
We can't even get close,

505
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,640
let alone make a connection.

506
00:25:07,244 --> 00:25:08,555
Now that you mention it,

507
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,350
it reminds me of someone

508
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:14,000
among us

509
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:15,488
who's made a connection.

510
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:17,390
Who?

511
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:19,444
You.

512
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:21,190
Don't you remember?

513
00:25:22,977 --> 00:25:24,511
The Right Chancellor asked

514
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:25,960
to build a canopy

515
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,440
for His Majesty's favorite peony,

516
00:25:27,955 --> 00:25:29,440
but the branches got damaged.

517
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:31,070
You were the one who saved it

518
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,110
and the Right Chancellor.

519
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:34,533
That was a huge service.

520
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:38,440
Now that the peony is thriving,

521
00:25:38,866 --> 00:25:40,990
the Right Chancellor is pleased
every time he sees it,

522
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,550
and he even mentioned you.

523
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:47,110
He surely remembers
what you did for him.

524
00:25:53,711 --> 00:25:56,000
How could I ever get to see
the Right Chancellor?

525
00:25:59,070 --> 00:25:59,910
If I recall,

526
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:02,666
your appointment as the Litchi Envoy

527
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:04,311
was signed by him.

528
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,310
If you report it to him,

529
00:26:06,355 --> 00:26:07,800
it's not considered overstepping.

530
00:26:08,030 --> 00:26:09,720
Besides, the delivery

531
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:10,750
has proven doable.

532
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,880
He'll likely be pleased

533
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,711
and not blame you.

534
00:26:16,844 --> 00:26:18,555
After the Beginning of Spring,

535
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,680
Right Chancellor always comes

536
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,270
to visit the Leyou Garden.

537
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:25,160
Each time, he asks the person on duty

538
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,880
to report about that peony.

539
00:26:29,350 --> 00:26:31,920
That may be your chance.

540
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:39,550
When's his next visit?

541
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:42,333
As usual, it's today.

542
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:47,520
Liangyuan.

543
00:26:49,622 --> 00:26:50,720
Take this and give it a try.

544
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,377
Don't be late.

545
00:27:07,510 --> 00:27:08,350
Go on.

546
00:27:23,333 --> 00:27:24,430
Yes, Sir.

547
00:28:19,955 --> 00:28:21,080
What happened?

548
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:23,160
Mr. Li, you're back.

549
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,720
The peony is infested with bugs.

550
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:25,910
It's infested?

551
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:26,840
Mr. Li,

552
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:28,160
please help us.

553
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:28,960
Mr. Li,

554
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,830
please help us.

555
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,422
Please help us.

556
00:28:30,444 --> 00:28:30,880
Get up.

557
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:31,560
What's going on?

558
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,680
Didn't Mr. Song tell you?

559
00:28:34,022 --> 00:28:35,400
It was his shift today,

560
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:36,350
but when he saw

561
00:28:36,350 --> 00:28:37,240
the infested peony,

562
00:28:37,266 --> 00:28:39,844
he feared Right Chancellor
might blame him, so he ran off scared.

563
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,270
Who would've thought

564
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:43,733
he'd push you to take the blame?

565
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:48,830
These scoundrels.

566
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:51,390
I thought

567
00:28:52,177 --> 00:28:53,160
even the cruelest person

568
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,400
should have a conscience.

569
00:28:55,310 --> 00:28:58,000
I didn't expect them to be this vile.

570
00:28:58,790 --> 00:29:00,720
Mr. Li, please help us.

571
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,000
Well,

572
00:29:03,355 --> 00:29:04,960
is the Right Chancellor coming today?

573
00:29:05,350 --> 00:29:06,350
He'll be here after noon,

574
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,390
as usual.

