00:29:08,590 --> 00:29:09,880
we're done for.

577
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,440
Mr. Li, help us.

578
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:11,880
Get up.

579
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,750
Hurry and get up.

580
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:13,510
Please help us.

581
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,350
Get up. Quick.

582
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:15,240
Let me have a look.

583
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,000
Get up.

584
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,070
Come on.

585
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:19,200
Why are we here

586
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,422
at Leyou Garden today?

587
00:29:21,790 --> 00:29:22,630
Have you heard?

588
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:24,920
His Majesty casually mentioned

589
00:29:25,422 --> 00:29:26,911
the flowers were about to bloom.

590
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:29,070
He must be thinking

591
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:30,844
of visiting.

592
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:33,310
The Right Chancellor
frequents the garden

593
00:29:33,830 --> 00:29:36,888
because he's watching it
for His Majesty.

594
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:38,630
Now

595
00:29:39,270 --> 00:29:40,110
is the perfect time.

596
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:44,466
If he reports this to His Majesty,

597
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:47,160
it will surely please him.

598
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,920
Why don't we just

599
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,444
tell the Right Chancellor directly?

600
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:55,000
He's feeling unwell today.

601
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,880
Since we wish

602
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,160
to earn his favor,

603
00:29:58,733 --> 00:30:01,155
we'll have to be thoughtful.

604
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,350
We'll keep watch

605
00:30:02,790 --> 00:30:04,680
