606
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,480
Then report it

607
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,270
to him.

608
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:11,400
Wouldn't that please him even more?

609
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:13,000
That way...

610
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:17,760
That way,

611
00:30:17,977 --> 00:30:19,800
we gain the Right Chancellor's favor,

612
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:21,880
and he gains His Majesty's favor.

613
00:30:22,222 --> 00:30:23,577
If His Majesty is pleased,

614
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,550
we're all happy.

615
00:30:25,311 --> 00:30:26,955
Attendant Yu, your thoughtfulness

616
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:28,377
is unmatched in the palace.

617
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,440
The Right Chancellor is unwell,

618
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,822
and everyone's trying to impress him.

619
00:30:35,977 --> 00:30:37,577
The Imperial Academy of Medicine alone

620
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:40,022
