00:30:42,022 --> 00:30:43,160
attentively waiting on him

623
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:44,310
and bringing tonics.

624
00:30:44,310 --> 00:30:46,355
They've worn a path at his door.

625
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:49,720
However,

626
00:30:50,590 --> 00:30:52,240
only a few

627
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:55,750
truly understand

628
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:58,110
his needs.

629
00:31:01,288 --> 00:31:02,888
Thank you for your guidance, Sir.

630
00:31:02,933 --> 00:31:04,244
That was very educational.

631
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,110
What's wrong, Sir?

632
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,550
What's that smell?

