00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,590
Leyou Garden is an imperial garden.

650
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:07,311
You've turned it into a smoky mess.

651
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:10,270
Fortunately, the Right Chancellor
isn't coming

652
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:11,844
due to his sick condition. If he were

653
00:32:11,888 --> 00:32:13,733
to breathe this smoke,
you'd lose your head!

654
00:32:16,555 --> 00:32:18,244
The Right Chancellor isn't coming?

655
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:21,350
Attendant Yu,

656
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:22,550
