657
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:33,866
I think I've seen you somewhere.

658
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:35,920
I'm Li Shande from the Shanglin Office.

659
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:37,977
Greetings, Attendant Yu.

660
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:41,920
I once asked you

661
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,244
about how to transport fresh litchis.

662
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,270
A death

663
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:49,030
can put paid to this mission.

664
00:32:50,070 --> 00:32:51,160
People

665
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,270
would understand.

666
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:57,955
You didn't die.

667
00:32:58,510 --> 00:32:59,550
Any progress

668
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:00,910
on your mission?

669
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:04,377
The transport isn't a problem now,

670
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:05,830
but no office

671
00:33:05,888 --> 00:33:07,311
will accept my petition.

672
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:11,160
Perhaps you were right.

673
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:12,640
Only if I die

674
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,622
can the mission end.

675
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,266
Judging by what you said,

676
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:21,830
the fresh litchis

677
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,680
won't reach His Majesty after all.

678
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:25,520
No.

679
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,622
The litchi delivery is feasible,

680
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:29,920
but it has to go through

681
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,070
every office

682
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:32,311
for approval.

683
00:33:34,510 --> 00:33:35,640
You may not know.

684
00:33:36,070 --> 00:33:36,910
That process

685
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:41,688
takes at least a month.

686
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:42,630
That won't do.

687
00:33:43,488 --> 00:33:45,688
Noble Consort's birthday
is on the first day of June.

688
00:33:45,810 --> 00:33:47,050
We can't wait a month.

689
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:50,790
Do you know why

690
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:52,270
His Majesty appointed a special envoy

691
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:54,755
who's above all offices?

692
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,960
He wanted it done

693
00:33:58,270 --> 00:33:58,880
as soon

694
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,733
as he ordered.

695
00:34:03,310 --> 00:34:04,310
And yet

696
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:08,066
you're still stuck.

697
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,440
No one actually

698
00:34:13,755 --> 00:34:15,777
follows the imperial decree.

699
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,280
Well.

700
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,710
As the vice purchasing commissioner,

701
00:34:25,355 --> 00:34:27,533
my duty is to procure goods
for the inner court.

702
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:30,630
If fresh litchis from Gaozhou

703
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:33,070
is what His Majesty desires,

704
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:35,630
I'll help you

705
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:38,777
bypass those complex procedures.

706
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:40,880
You're really helping me?

707
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:44,070
If I could share His Majesty's burden,

708
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:48,377
I'll see it through to the end.

709
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,030
But I heard

710
00:34:54,755 --> 00:34:57,022
litchis lose their color,
fragrance, and flavor

711
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,800
after three days.

712
00:34:59,510 --> 00:35:00,350
Are you sure

713
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,630
they can be delivered fresh?

714
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:10,630
Have a look at this.

715
00:35:10,866 --> 00:35:13,044
Here's the litchi delivery method
I came up with.

716
00:35:15,777 --> 00:35:17,266
All the details are stated here.

717
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:30,230
This is indeed brilliant.

718
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:33,510
But

719
00:35:34,622 --> 00:35:36,555
I must return to the palace at once.

720
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:39,480
May I take this back
and study it carefully?

721
00:35:39,755 --> 00:35:41,133
If I don't understand something,

722
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,977
I'll come to see you tomorrow.

723
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,000
What time?

724
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:45,840
Tomorrow,

725
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:47,622
10 o'clock in the morning.

726
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:49,030
We'll meet here.

727
00:35:50,133 --> 00:35:51,160
Yes, Sir.

728
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,000
Attendant Yu?

729
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,120
Liangyuan,

730
00:35:57,670 --> 00:35:59,550
why didn't you consult me first?

731
00:36:00,266 --> 00:36:02,577
None of the offices
accepted my petition.

732
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:04,311
He was the only one willing to help me.

733
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:10,070
Attendant Yu is a newly promoted eunuch

734
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:11,710
in the inner court.

735
00:36:12,110 --> 00:36:13,440
He's cunning

736
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,800
and always steals credit.

737
00:36:14,977 --> 00:36:17,155
Everyone calls him
"Softshell Turtle On Top".

738
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:18,390
What does that mean?

739
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,480
It means he's like a softshell turtle,

740
00:36:20,590 --> 00:36:21,670
once he bites,

741
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,710
he won't let go.

742
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:26,333
Then why is it "on top"?

743
00:36:27,111 --> 00:36:28,600
He's an eunuch, that's why.

744
00:36:31,333 --> 00:36:32,800
You should've been extra careful

745
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,150
dealing with him.

746
00:36:35,110 --> 00:36:36,239
Woe to you.

747
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:38,070
Now that he's taken
your litchi delivery method,

748
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,400
he could just use it as his own

749
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:41,644
and head to Lingnan
to transport fresh litchis back.

750
00:36:41,644 --> 00:36:42,230
That way,

751
00:36:42,288 --> 00:36:44,355
all the credit will go to him.

752
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:46,320
You'll be cut out of everything.

753
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,600
No way.

754
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,030
He said

755
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:54,190
he wanted to take the petition back
and study it.

756
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:55,510
We agreed to meet again tomorrow

757
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:56,510
at Leyou Garden.

758
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:57,880
You believed him?

759
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,888
He won't come tomorrow.

760
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:04,110
It can't be.

761
00:37:04,911 --> 00:37:06,480
I've been to every office.

762
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,670
They can testify

763
00:37:07,670 --> 00:37:08,920
the litchi delivery method

764
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:10,190
was my work.

765
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,320
Liangyuan,

766
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:19,066
when it comes to arithmetic,

767
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:20,933
you're an expert.

768
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,670
But in official dealings,

769
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:27,200
you're worse than a child.

770
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:28,550
Those offices

771
00:37:28,550 --> 00:37:30,070
wouldn't accept your petition.

772
00:37:30,222 --> 00:37:31,440
Why would they testify for you?

773
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:33,644
They'd rather stay out of trouble.

774
00:37:33,666 --> 00:37:35,244
Also, no one wants to offend

775
00:37:35,711 --> 00:37:38,400
that "Softshell Turtle On Top"
over a thankless task.

776
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,070
How have you

777
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:41,070
not learned your lesson

778
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,480
after being schemed against

779
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:44,422
since you returned from Lingnan?

780
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,190
I spent

781
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:48,510
all my effort

782
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:50,070
on the litchi delivery method.

783
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:51,360
I didn't have the energy

784
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:52,755
to bother with all that politics.

785
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,933
If you'd attached an appreciation note

786
00:38:01,955 --> 00:38:03,440
when you handed in your method,

787
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:05,030
mentioning

788
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:06,509
the efforts of the Lingnan commissioner

789
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,410
and support from
the Bureau of General Accounts,

790
00:38:08,410 --> 00:38:10,888
the Court of the Imperial Treasury,
the Bureau of Agriculture,

791
00:38:10,888 --> 00:38:12,044
and the Imperial Kitchen,

792
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:14,422
then Attendant Yu wouldn't
dare to steal your credit.

793
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,630
Liangyuan, official dealings

794
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:20,288
boil down to three things.

795
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,880
Blend into the crowd, share the credit,

796
00:38:23,066 --> 00:38:25,800
and make even the lightest work
seem like a collective effort.

797
00:38:25,888 --> 00:38:27,510
If you take all the credit for yourself,

798
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:29,600
you won't last long.

799
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,088
I've spent months climbing,

800
00:38:37,022 --> 00:38:39,177
and just when I was about to
reach the top,

801
00:38:39,244 --> 00:38:40,511
I slipped

802
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:42,600
and fell into a pit again.

803
00:38:42,622 --> 00:38:43,622
Exactly.

804
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:46,880
Too bad

805
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,244
I'm just a low-ranking clerk,

806
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:50,133
and I'm too straightforward.

807
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,670
I only associate

808
00:38:51,670 --> 00:38:53,155
with you and Zimei.

809
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:54,440
Now

810
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:56,466
I can see what's going on,

811
00:38:56,622 --> 00:38:58,977
but I have no way to help you out of it

812
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:02,711
or resolve your problem.

813
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,350
Maybe

814
00:39:07,911 --> 00:39:10,133
you should make arrangements
for your daughter.

815
00:39:10,711 --> 00:39:12,320
