816
00:39:12,710 --> 00:39:13,550
Adopt?

817
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:15,360
What are you on about?

818
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,320
Who can I give her to?

819
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,711
You?

820
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:19,590
I'm not giving her to anyone.

821
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:21,320
No way.

822
00:39:23,044 --> 00:39:24,822
That softshell turtle
wouldn't do that to me.

823
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:25,680
Dig in.

824
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,120
Attendant Yu,

825
00:39:35,670 --> 00:39:37,230
