832
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:02,880
He's indeed talented

833
00:40:04,422 --> 00:40:06,244
to come up with such a method.

834
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,070
It's

835
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,288
very complicated.

836
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,670
It takes meticulous calculations

837
00:40:14,177 --> 00:40:16,044
