838
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,510
I can tell

839
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:23,440
it's been tested and refined

840
00:40:23,511 --> 00:40:25,400
through multiple attempts in Lingnan.

841
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:32,190
This task

842
00:40:33,533 --> 00:40:35,155
has to be him.

843
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:38,911
Please enlighten me.

844
00:40:39,190 --> 00:40:41,311
Why haven't you gone to meet him yet?

845
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,840
The more urgent the matter,

846
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:49,022
