851
00:41:11,844 --> 00:41:12,670
No one's coming.

852
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:13,760
Right.

853
00:41:22,066 --> 00:41:24,000
(Like a fish in the pond.)

854
00:41:26,190 --> 00:41:27,440
(Starve it for a few days)

855
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:30,000
(to make it anxious)

856
00:41:30,422 --> 00:41:31,510
(and desperate.)

857
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,480
When it's dying,

858
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:37,400
feed it a little,

859
00:41:39,030 --> 00:41:41,800
