00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:46,880
We'll starve

862
00:41:48,377 --> 00:41:50,244
the Litchi Envoy for a few days.

863
00:41:52,030 --> 00:41:53,880
Don't worry. He won't die.

864
00:41:56,190 --> 00:41:59,288
Anyway, the petition is with me.

865
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,230
This fish

866
00:42:03,911 --> 00:42:05,230
is mine.

867
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:41,530
=The Litchi Road=

868
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,390
Just say it.

869
00:42:43,711 --> 00:42:45,111
What do you want me to do?

870
00:42:45,155 --> 00:42:47,733
Did you keep the evidence
I told you to gather?

871
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:48,760
Don't worry.

872
00:42:49,070 --> 00:42:49,910
It's in safe hands.

873
00:42:58,150 --> 00:42:59,440
Was it me who wanted litchis?

874
00:42:59,670 --> 00:43:00,630
Was it?

875
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,110
It was His Majesty.

876
00:43:03,155 --> 00:43:04,088
It was Right Chancellor.

877
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:05,533
It was Right Chancellor's sister.

878
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:06,670
It was your sister.

879
00:43:06,866 --> 00:43:07,840
Fine, I give up.

880
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:18,760
The Han emperor longed for a beauty
to rival a nation

881
00:43:23,420 --> 00:43:28,770
For years he ruled,
yet couldn't find one

882
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:38,110
A girl from the Yang family
came of age

883
00:43:38,270 --> 00:43:41,780
Raised in her chamber,
unknown to the world

884
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:45,600
Born with stunning grace
she couldn't hide

885
00:43:45,700 --> 00:43:49,320
One day, she was chosen
to serve by his side

886
00:43:56,660 --> 00:44:01,940
She glanced back
with a smile of myriad charms

887
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:07,380
All the palace beauties
lost their glow

888
00:44:13,100 --> 00:44:16,790
In the chilly spring,
she bathed at Huaqing Pond

889
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,780
The warm spring water
slid over her silky skin

890
00:44:23,990 --> 00:44:27,710
Handmaids helped her rise
from the water

891
00:44:27,710 --> 00:44:31,860
Thus began the time
she gained the emperor's favor

892
00:44:34,980 --> 00:44:38,600
Flowing hair, a flower-bright face,
and a hairpin of glamour

893
00:44:38,600 --> 00:44:42,410
In the warm lotus canopy,
they spent spring nights together

894
00:44:44,130 --> 00:44:47,930
Those sweet nights were too short,
he rose until noon

895
00:44:47,930 --> 00:44:53,740
From then on,
he skipped the morning court

896
00:45:00,720 --> 00:45:04,380
Always at his side,
forever delighting and dining

897
00:45:04,380 --> 00:45:07,910
They spent spring on spring outings,
night on night together

898
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:13,860
In the palace
lived three thousand beauties

899
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:20,340
Yet all three thousand favors
were hers alone
